  "texts": [
    "This process provides a zero-shot way of determining the parameters typically trained in prompt tuning.",
    "In contrast, 500xCompressor is more akin to prefix tuning.",
    "Here, the inputs for the decoder are not embeddings, but KV pairs, which are determined by the fine-tuned LLM encoder.",
    "These KV pairs contain more parameters than embeddings and are assumed to store richer details (Li and Liang, 2021).",
    "500xCompressor proves that KV pairs can compress more detailed information at high compression ratios and outperform embeddings in terms of data retention (Li et al., 2024)."
  ],
